To those giving this app negative reviews after the latest update, stop. The app itself still functions exactly as designed, with little to no bugs, and is a beautiful icon pack. That being said, I too did not like the size increase of the icons, but a simple fix is going into your custom launcher settings and resizing the icons. For example, if you use Nova Launcher like I do, use the following. Nova Launcher Settings -> Desktop -> Icon Layout. I dropped the size percentage from 100% to 70% and it's exactly as before. Same beautiful icon pack, easily back to the size it was before the update. Don't be so quick to complain when there's nothing wrong except your ability to search for a solution. Thanks to the developer for a fabulous icon pack!
